00:01:29.220 --> 00:01:32.890
Seiza no matataki kazoe

00:01:32.890 --> 00:01:36.140
Aşkın kaderini tahmin ediyorlar

00:01:32.890 --> 00:01:36.140
Uranau koi no yukue

00:01:36.140 --> 00:01:39.390
Tam da burada doğdum

00:01:36.140 --> 00:01:39.390
Onaji kuni ni umareta no

