00:12:47.850 --> 00:12:48.360
Kahretsin!

00:12:49.650 --> 00:12:51.580
Karışırsan yaralanırsın!

00:12:57.550 --> 00:12:59.040
Ne yapıyorsun?

00:12:59.750 --> 00:13:00.870
Fena değil.

00:13:01.310 --> 00:13:02.250
Barbarca.

00:13:15.270 --> 00:13:18.850
