00:13:20.190 --> 00:13:23.230
Mako! Vay, neler oluyor?! Kavga mı?!

00:13:24.070 --> 00:13:24.850
Kahretsin!

00:13:24.850 --> 00:13:25.480
Bekle!

00:13:25.480 --> 00:13:26.530
